{"type":"message","id":"5d8f9131","parentId":"07e00e56","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:56:05.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户开始了新会话，我需要按照启动序列执行。根据 AGENTS.md，需要读取：\n1. SOUL.md - 我是谁\n2. USER.md - 用户信息\n3. memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (今天和昨天) - 最近上下文\n4. MEMORY.md - 长期记忆（仅主会话）\n\n然后用设定的个性打招呼，问用户想做什么。\n\n当前模型是 minimax/MiniMax-M2.5，default_model 是 custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus，所以应该提及默认模型。\n\n先读取必要的文件。\n","thinkingSignature":"be47acda2f02ffa4228f342f485d18f9f0cd4b8dd486844c05bc74beb94672c1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rq8wtlv8bbc3_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/memory/2026-03-27.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rq8wtlv8bbc3_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/workspace-fox-openclaw_ai/memory/2026-03-26.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":13264,"output":214,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13670,"cost":{"input":0.0039792,"output":0.0002568,"cacheRead":0.000005759999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004241759999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774583754841,"responseId":"061532cb7182b3f0087888f3cccaef99"}}
